episodes.title: Friend of landlord killed by 'Zizian' member recalls 'kindhearted person'
episodes.description:
A Solano County landlord who survived being attacked in 2022 was killed in a second attack earlier this year. Months later, friends of Curtis Lind are still trying to figure out what drove a person tied to a cult-like group known as the Zizians to stab him to death.
